---
description: Entry rule for the lightweight AI-DLC Harness (Product Discovery, Inception, and Construction).
alwaysApply: false
---

For Product Discovery, use `/ux-product-discovery-lite`.

Use `/aidlc-inception-lite` only when `product-discovery/product-hypothesis.md` is approved by the human.

Use `/aidlc-construction-lite` only when `reviews/inception-exit-review.md` is `Approved`.

Stop at Construction Exit. Do not proceed to Operations in this Harness; Operations requires a separate, explicit human request.

For detailed procedures, use the Skill definitions under `.agents/skills/`.
